ame":"mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-black/45 p-6 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3 font-semibold text-purple-400 md:text-2xl","children":"The Challenge"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":"NOVASPHERE 2026 is a dynamic inter-college innovation summit designed to ignite bold thinking and breakthrough ideas. It brings together the brightest young minds to pitch visionary concepts, design compelling visual solutions, engage in high-impact tech debates, and conquer real-time debugging battles."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":"Across four flagship events — Ideathon, Quantum Canvas, TechX Debate, Tech Escape Challenge and Debug Domain — participants will test their creativity, analytical thinking, technical knowledge, and presentation mastery in a celebration of ideas over execution."}]]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-black/45 p-6 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3 font-semibold text-purple-400 md:text-2xl","children":"The Opportunity"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":"With exciting prizes, prestigious recognition, and a platform to showcase your intellectual brilliance, NOVASPHERE 2026 empowers you to step into the spotlight."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":"Present your ideas before expert panels, compete with the sharpest innovators, expand your network, and build the confidence to transform concepts into future realities."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":"This isn’t just a competition — it’s where ideas find their voice and innovators find their stage."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"rounded-3xl border border-cyan-500/20 bg-black/45 p-6 md:p-10","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-purple-400 md:text-4xl","children":"The Learning Experience"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75 md:text-base","children":"At NovaSphere 2026, learning goes beyond listening — it's about building. Both workshops are fully hands-on, meaning participants won't just watch demonstrations; they will actively create, experiment, and develop real working outputs during the session. These workshops are structured to ensure every participant leaves with practical experience and tangible results."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-black/45 p-6 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-purple-400 md:text-xl","children":"🤖 AI Tools Workshop"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-cyan-200/80","children":"Hands-On Innovation with No-Code & AI Platforms"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"The AI Tools Workshop is a practical, build-focused session where participants will actively create AI-powered solutions using modern no-code and low-code platforms. With a special focus on tools like Antigravity and similar rapid-development ecosystems, this workshop empowers participants to transform ideas into working digital solutions — live during the session."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"Instead of theory-heavy explanations, the session follows a guided build format. Participants will be given a real-world problem and will step-by-step construct a solution using AI-assisted tools. From designing workflows to integrating automation and smart features, every attendee will work directly on their own system."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 font-semibold text-white/85","children":"During the workshop, participants will:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Build a functional AI-powered mini application."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Use drag-and-drop interfaces to create workflows."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Implement automation without writing complex code."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Integrate AI-generated content or logic."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Test and refine their digital solution in real time."}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"By the end of the session, participants will have a working prototype and a clear understanding of how modern AI platforms accelerate innovation. The focus is on execution, experimentation, and rapid creation — giving attendees a real builder's mindset."}]]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-black/45 p-6 text-sm leading-7 text-white/75","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-purple-400 md:text-xl","children":"🌐 Web Development Workshop"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-cyan-200/80","children":"Hands-On Web App Development from Scratch"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"The Web Development Workshop is designed as an interactive coding session where participants build a responsive web application step-by-step. This is not a passive lecture — attendees will code along in real time, gaining direct experience in structuring, styling, and making a website functional."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"Participants will start with a blank project and progressively develop a complete, responsive web page. The session focuses on clarity, structure, and modern practices while ensuring that every concept is immediately applied through hands-on coding."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 font-semibold text-white/85","children":"During the workshop, participants will:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Write and str